
  PC Key                 MSX Key / Function
  ---------------------  ------------------

  ' / "                  * / @
  2 / @                  2 / "
  8 / *                  8 / '
  ] / }                  [ / ]
  [ / {                  ' / `
  ; / :                  ~ / ^
  / / ?                  ; / :
  \ / |                  { / }
  R Control              / / ?
# R Control              <DeadKey>

  L Control              <Control>

  R Alt                  <Code> / <Kana>
  L Alt                  <Graph

  R Super                <Yes>
  L Super                <No>

  Control + F1           toggle grabinput
  Control + F2           toggle all trainer cheats
  Control + F3           toggle scale (1/2)

  F6                     toggle osd keyboard
  F7                     <Select>
  F8                     <Stop>

  F9 pressed             throttle off
  F9 released            throttle on

  F10                    toggle console display

  F11                    quick savestate (to   'quicksave' slot)
  F12                    quick loadstate (from 'quicksave' slot)

  Shift   + PrintScreen  capture doublesize raw screenshot
  Control + PrintScreen  capture scaled screenshot with osd

  Home                   start doublesize screen recording
  End                    stop  doublesize screen recording

  PageUp                 backward 1 sec in time, using the reverse feature
  PageDown               forward  1 sec in time, using the reverse feature

  Menu                   toggle osd menu
  Alt + Enter            toggle full screen mode
  ScrollLock             toggle audio mute

  Pause                  pause emulation

  Control + Shift + Del  machine reset

  Control + Pause        quit emulator (not in Windows)
  Alt + F4               quit emulator

